[[File:پل رودخانه مند.JPG|200px|right|thumb|Mond River]] '''Mond protected area''' is a {{Convert|46000|ha|adj=on}} [[plain]] and [[desert]] [[protected area]] on the [[Persian Gulf]] coast of the [[Bord Khun District]], [[Deyr County]], [[Bushehr Province]] in southern [[Iran]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.protectedplanet.net/mond-protected-area |title=Mond |publisher=Protected Planet |date= |accessdate=2016-01-26}}</ref> The protected area was established in 1976. The [[Mond River]] empties into the Persian Gulf in the northern part of the area.<ref>{{citation |title=Mond protected area |first=Mahmood |last=Moqimi |location=Bushehr, Iran |date=2004 |page=57}}</ref><ref>{{citation |title=Biodiversity of Mond Protected Area |first=Hossein |last=Mostafavi |publisher=Shahid Beheshti University |location=Tehran, Iran |date=2008 |pages=252–3}}</ref>
