'''Travno''' is an [[urban settlement]] of the [[Croatia|Croatian]] capital of [[Zagreb]], located in a city district of [[Novi Zagreb – istok]].
It is one of the most densely populated settlements in Croatia mostly due to the largest dwelling house in Croatia: [[Mamutica]].
